    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cinemas with ornate architecture and interior decoration, emerging in the 1920s. The exterior of the movie palace is often outfitted with a marquee and an upright, showcasing the cinema's name.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
